<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>rclone on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/rclone/</link><description>Recent content in rclone on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/rclone/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>tgdrive/rclone</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/tgdrive-rclone/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/tgdrive-rclone/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="개요"&gt;개요&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%ea%b0%9c%ec%9a%94" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id="패키지-설치"&gt;패키지 설치 &lt;sup id="fnref:1"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%ed%8c%a8%ed%82%a4%ec%a7%80-%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install -y unzip &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; curl -sSL instl.vercel.app/rclone &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; bash &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; sudo dnf remove -y unzip
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="crond"&gt;crond&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#crond" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;호스트 간 데이터 이동 &lt;sup id="fnref:2"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:2" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#5e81ac;font-style:italic"&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#5e81ac;font-style:italic"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# rclone으로 이동&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;source&lt;/span&gt; /home/dev/.bashrc
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;source&lt;/span&gt; /home/dev/.local/bin/utils.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;log_file&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/home/dev/.local/log/&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;basename &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$0&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sed &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;s/.sh//&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.log
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;msg_file&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/home/dev/.local/log/&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;basename &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$0&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sed &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;s/.sh//&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.tmp
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /dev/null &amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$log_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;flock -n /tmp/rclone.lock &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; rclone move &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$1&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$2&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; --config /home/dev/.config/rclone/rclone.conf &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; --log-file &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$log_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --log-level DEBUG &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; --delete-empty-src-dirs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;grep -oE &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;^Transferred:.*100%.*\/s&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$log_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; head -n &lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sed &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;s/\t//g&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sed &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;s/ */ /g&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$msg_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;send_tel_msg &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$TEL_BOT_KEY&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$TEL_CHAT_ID&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$msg_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;rm &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$msg_file&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;구성 백업 &lt;sup id="fnref:3"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:3" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>vsftpd</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/vsftpd/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/vsftpd/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="포트-개방"&gt;포트 개방&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%ed%8f%ac%ed%8a%b8-%ea%b0%9c%eb%b0%a9" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo firewall-cmd --permanent --add-forward-port&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;port&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;6****:proto&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;tcp:toport&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;21&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo firewall-cmd --permanent --add-port&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;6****-6****/tcp &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo firewall-cmd --reload &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo firewall-cmd --list-all
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="selinux-구성"&gt;selinux 구성&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#selinux-%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%b1" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;/home directory, symbolic link, passive mode를 허용.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;selinux Permissive mode인 경우에도 영향 있으므로 반드시 구성.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo setsebool -P ftpd_use_passive_mode on &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo setsebool -P ftpd_full_access on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="설치"&gt;설치&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install -y vsftpd &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo systemctl &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;enable&lt;/span&gt; vsftpd &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo systemctl start vsftpd &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo systemctl status vsftpd
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo cp /etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf /etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf.bak &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo cp /etc/vsftpd/ftpusers /etc/vsftpd/ftpusers.bak
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;root 접속 허용 (optional)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>